WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.066 --> 00:00:01.300
Prompting marriage with me?

2
00:00:01.533 --> 00:00:03.900
No, Chen Hao, what do you mean?

3
00:00:03.900 --> 00:00:06.066
If you want to break off the marriage, we will refund to you later.

4
00:00:06.066 --> 00:00:07.666
It's up to you to return, why can't I return it?

5
00:00:07.666 --> 00:00:09.366
Because you are a poor boy with nothing

6
00:00:09.366 --> 00:00:10.600
It's not worthy of Wanwan at all

7
00:00:11.266 --> 00:00:13.100
Yes, for you.

8
00:00:13.100 --> 00:00:15.133
You are the high-ranking eldest lady

9
00:00:15.133 --> 00:00:16.700
I, Chen Hao, am a toad

10
00:00:16.700 --> 00:00:18.300
Not worthy of you white swans

11
00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:20.566
But I tell you, no matter how poor I am

12
00:00:20.566 --> 00:00:22.200
My pride and dignity

13
00:00:22.266 --> 00:00:23.966
It's not something you can trample on at will

14
00:00:23.966 --> 00:00:26.266
Chen Hao, I'm sorry.

15
00:00:26.266 --> 00:00:29.066
I was really abrupt yesterday.

16
00:00:29.066 --> 00:00:30.233
But

17
00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:32.200
I don't agree to divorce

18
00:00:32.200 --> 00:00:34.966
Why? I just don't agree.

19
00:00:34.966 --> 00:00:36.066
But I think it's enough to return.

20
00:00:36.066 --> 00:00:37.766
Chen Hao, are you a fool?

21
00:00:37.766 --> 00:00:38.766
Can't you see?

22
00:00:38.766 --> 00:00:40.200
Why don't you often accept divorce?

23
00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:41.466
If you were a man

24
00:00:41.466 --> 00:00:43.700
This marriage should be returned by our woman

25
00:00:46.400 --> 00:00:50.966
Chen Hao, will you come to see me again?

26
00:00:51.533 --> 00:00:52.333
Yes.

27
00:01:13.766 --> 00:01:14.566
What!

